  <main>
    <div class="page-section bg-light">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-lg-8 py-3">
            <div class="blog-single-wrap">
              <div class="post-thumbnail">
                <img src="/img/course/{{course_detail.id}}.jpg" alt="">
              </div>
              <h1 class="post-title">{{course_detail.name}}</h1>
              <div class="post-meta">
                <div class="post-author">
                  <a href="#">
                      {{#each this.teacher}}
                          {{this.fullname}}  
                      {{/each}} 
                  </a>  
                </div>
                <span class="gap">|</span>
                <div class="post-date">
                  <a href="#">{{course_detail.modification_date}}</a>
                </div>
                <span class="gap">|</span>
                <div>
                  <a href="#">{{num_of_member.member}} Học viên </a>
                </div>
                <span class="gap">|</span>
                <div class="post-comment-count">
                  <a href="#">{{rating.num_of_rating}} Bình luận</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="post-content">
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Provident, magnam aliquam sit tempora atque numquam, porro autem eius in odio quos nisi sequi doloribus, quo ipsam labore corrupti mollitia! Quos.</p>
